sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Ag as Agent
    participant Mcp as MCP server
    participant H as PARCS Host
    participant D as Daemon pool
    Ag->>Mcp: get_cluster_info
    Mcp-->>Ag: {maxParallelism: 21, …}
    Ag->>Mcp: create_session(sourceCode)
    Mcp->>Mcp: Roslyn compile
    Mcp-->>Ag: {sessionId}
    Ag->>Mcp: run_layer(sessionId, parallelism=20)
    Mcp->>H: submit job
    H->>D: scale-out via KEDA
    D-->>H: per-worker JSON outputs
    H-->>Mcp: aggregated resultJson
    Mcp-->>Ag: {layerId, status:"Completed", result}
    Ag->>Mcp: run_layer(sessionId, parallelism=1, previousLayerId)
    Mcp->>Mcp: fetch stored result by layerId
    Mcp->>H: submit aggregator job
    H->>D: single worker
    D-->>H: final answer
    H-->>Mcp: aggregated resultJson
    Mcp-->>Ag: {final result}
